Today’s field trip was a little disappointing bc I didn’t find too many new items 🫤- admittedly my expectations are always higher here bc they tend to carry more Asian items. Maybe next time🤞

📍Costco in Duluth, GA

New items - @lole fleece belt bag, and @imuraya.usa Japanese castella cake (sponge cake) 🍰 is back again! 

Just a few clearance items to highlight - @stearnsandfoster mattress protector (lowest price I’ve seen - others selling at higher clearance prices), @laterrafina cherry and jalapeño dip and spread, and they still carry the beachcomber bags (just the blue ones). FYI I saw a few boxes of the old @gourmia air fryer but prices aren’t marked - I’m guessing they’re fetching a good deal on them.
